:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
A payment card is one of the most secure means of payment
available, and misuse in connection with payments made using
Dankort cards is minimal. You can help to make the system even
safer by following this good advice.
.br
.tp 5mm 10mm
¤1.¤Good advice for Dankort cards
.br
¤2.¤Good advice when using Visa/Dankort cards abroad
.br
¤3.¤If your Dankort card is lost or stolen
.br
¤4.¤Find out more on the Internet
.sp 5mm
:SWISS10.
:FED.
1.¤Good advice for Dankort cards
:SKRSLUT.
.sp 3mm
:SWISS8.
:FED.
Before use
:SKRSLUT.
.br
*¤Consider
.in 5mm nobreak
your Dankort and Visa/Dankort cards to be hard cash - and keep them in
a safe place both at home and when you are travelling. For example, never
leave them lying around in the open.
.in 0mm
.br
*¤Learn
.in 5mm nobreak
your PIN code off by heart. If you are not sure that you can always
remember your code, use a PIN code reminder. You can download a PIN
code reminder from
.us www.dankort.dk
or pick one up from a branch of &BANKNAVN..
.in 0mm
.br
*¤Never
.in 5mm nobreak
reveal your PIN code to other people - it is personal, so you must keep it
to yourself.
.in 0mm
.br
*¤Never
.in 5mm nobreak
use your PIN code as a password or access code in other contexts.
.in 0mm
.sp 3mm
:FED.
During use
:SKRSLUT.
.br
*¤Protect
.in 5mm nobreak
your PIN code while you enter it. Do not let anyone see your code when you
enter it.
.in 0mm
.br
*¤Never
.in 5mm nobreak
sign a receipt unless it states the total sum paid.
.in 0mm
.br
*¤Always
.in 5mm nobreak
ask for a receipt, and keep it to check against your statement.
.in 0mm
.sp 3mm
:FED.
After use
:SKRSLUT.
.br
*¤Check
.in 5mm nobreak
the movements on your account via your netbanking solution or on your
account statement.
.in 0mm
.br
*¤Regularly
.in 5mm nobreak
check to make sure that you have not lost your card(s).
.in 0mm
.br
*¤Take
.in 5mm nobreak
immediate action if you have lost your card or suspect that it may have
been misused. Contact &BANKNAVN. or Nets without delay.
.in 0mm
.sp 5mm
:SWISS10.
:FED.
2.¤Good advice when using Visa/Dankort cards abroad
:SKRSLUT.
.sp 3mm
:SWISS8.
:FED.
Take care with using your PIN code
:SKRSLUT.
.br
Outside Denmark, you must only use your PIN code in ATMs, payment machines
and shops that display the VISA logo.
.sp 3mm
:FED.
Remember your passport
:SKRSLUT.
.br
Banks abroad will often ask to see your passport if you wish to take out a
cash advance.
.sp 5mm
:SWISS10.
:FED.
3.¤If your Dankort card is lost or stolen
:SKRSLUT.
.sp 3mm
:SWISS8.
If your Dankort or Visa/Dankort card is lost or stolen, report this
immediately. You must do the same if you suspect that someone had
learned your PIN code or that others are using your card or card number
inappropriately.
.br
Contact &BANKNAVN. or Nets immediately on:
.br
.in 15mm
.sp 3mm
telefon +45 44 89 29 29
.br
telefax +45 44 68 11 36
.sp 3mm
.in 0mm
State your name and address, the name of your bank and your card
number, account number or civil registration (CPR) number. This will
immediately block your Dankort card and prevent it being used.
.sp 5mm
:SWISS10.
:FED.
4.¤Find out more on the Internet
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
You can find out more on the Internet. See:
.br
.us www.crimprev.dk
.br
.us www.dankort.dk
.br
.us www.Nets.eu
.ar off
